items.text:
Vi søger skuespillere (25–33 år) med anden etnisk herkomst eller afrikaner til en mørk og visuelt ambitiøs musikvideo.

Tre venner finder et sted at overnatte – guidet af en app, der måske lytter lidt for godt.

Det der starter som sjov, bliver hurtigt til noget langt mere foruroligende.

KARAKTERE:

🔹 KAOS – fundet

🔹 BENDER – rolig, men uforudsigelig

🔹 KARMA – drømmende, fanget i sin egen verden

Projektet er ulønnet, men med høj kunstnerisk ambition og stærk visuel stil.

📩 Send headshots + kontaktinfo til elyascaster@gmail.com

items.text:
Hej alle sammen

Jeg søger en mandlig model til en kampagnevideo for vores rygsæk-brand. Der er ingen replikker, da videoen får musik og effekter som lydside, så det handler mest om tilstedeværelse og udtryk foran kameraet.

Optagelserne foregår i Århus. Projektet er på frivillig basis, men du får naturligvis det færdige materiale, som du også kan bruge til din egen portfolio.

Hvis det lyder som noget for dig, så kontakt mig over e-mail: Carlsjensen@icloud.com

På forhånd tak
Carl Schmidt Jensen

items.title: **Lønnet**

items.text:
**WARSZAWA 11 października**

**film fabularny - Rola Epizodyczna**

**Stawka: 1000 zł**

Do roli epizodycznej w filmie fabularnym JAN BO szukam młodej atrakcyjnej kobiety, która wystąpi w scenie - **topless**.

Bez kontrowersji. Jeden z bohaterów budzi się obok pięknej dziewczyny. Jest do połowy przykryta.

**Do zgłoszenia proszę załączyć wizytówkę jako link do YouTube.**

Ponieważ gramy lata 80te mamy nieuniknione wytyczne charakteryzacji:
* brak tatuaży 
* bez tuneli w uszach, kolczyków w wardze, nosie czy brwiach
* paznokcie TYLKO naturalne.
* bez permanentnych makijaży, doklejonych rzęs i  ingerencji medycyny estetycznej

**ZGŁOSZENIA**

Poproszę na adres: **ewelina.wika@podtytulem.pl**

W tytule: **GIRL**

W treści: imię i nazwisko, wiek, nr telefonu, miejscowość + wymiary: wzrost, klatka, pas, biodra, rozmiar ubrania i buta + wizytówka

W załączniku: ZDJĘCIE TWARZY I SYLWETKI (ubrane): tylko z dnia zgłoszenia.
* Portretowe selfie w dziennym świetle, na wprost, patrząc w obiektyw. Bez żadnych filtrów. Bez okularów. Bez nakrycia głowy.
* Bez makijażu, w rozpuszczonych włosach tak, żeby widoczna była długość włosów

items.title: **WARSZAWA 11 października**

items.text:
**WARSZAWA **

**10, 11, 13, 14 października**

**film fabularny**

Na kolejne dni filmu **JAN BO** i już jedne z ostatnich szukam Statystów jak poniżej. Przeczytajcie proszę uważnie wytyczne charakteryzacji.

**10 PAŹDZIERNIKA (piątek):**
* **MŁODZIEŻ NA PRÓBIE MUZYCZNEJ 18-25 LAT **- jedna scena, wnętrze. Głównie dziewczyny. Stawka: 120 zł gotówka po planie

**11 PAŹDZIERNIKA (sobota):**
* **POKOJÓWKA**- kobieta ok. 30-40 lat. Stawka 180 zł gotówką po planie (przymiarki stacjonarne: 60 zł + 120 zł za dzień zdjęciowy). Przymiarki w piątek 10.10 na Chełmskiej po 14:00 

**13 PAŹDZIERNIKA (poniedziałek):**
* **GOŚCIE BARU / PRZECHODNIE - wiek ok. 20-55 lat. **Jedna scena, godziny popołudniowe.** **Stawka 120 zł gotówką po planie
* **STRAŻNICY GRANICZNI - mężczyźni ok. 30-50 lat**. Jedna scena. Poproszę wymiary w zgłoszeniu. Stawka 140 zł gotówką po planie
* **STRAŻNIK GRANICZNY Z OWCZARKIEM NIEMIECKIM **- jak wyżej. Jedna scena. Stawka 180 zł gotówką po planie.
* **KELNERKA **- **kobieta ok. 20-35 lat**.Jedna scena. Stawka 120 zł gotówką po planie

**14 PAŹDZIERNIKA (wtorek):**
* **KOBIETA NA SPACERZE Z PSEM** - wiek bez znaczenia. Psiak nie może być rasowy. Kundle będą najlepsze. Poproszę zdjęcie psa również. **Jedna scena nocna. 240 zł przelewem**

Ponieważ gramy lata 80te mamy nieuniknione wytyczne charakteryzacji:

**Dla wszystkich:**
* brak tatuaży w widocznych miejscach (ręce również, na nogach u pań też odpadają)
* bez tuneli w uszach
* kolczyki w nosie, brwiach czy wardze trzeba wyjąć na zdjęcia

**Panowie:**
* bez wygolonych boków i bez włosów ścinanych maszynką, bez zarostów od barbera
* długie włosy super
* łysi panowie niestety odpadają

**Panie:**
* paznokcie TYLKO naturalne. 
* bez permanentnych makijaży, doklejonych rzęs i innych ingerencji współczesnych kosmetologii

**ZGŁOSZENIA**

Poproszę na adres: **dominika@podtytulem.pl**

W tytule: **JB + wybrane daty**

W treści: imię i nazwisko, wiek, nr telefonu, miejscowość + wymiary: wzrost, klatka, pas, biodra, rozmiar ubrania i buta

W załączniku: ZDJĘCIE TWARZY I SYLWETKI: tylko z dnia zgłoszenia.

Portretowe selfie w dziennym świetle, na wprost, patrząc w obiektyw. Bez żadnych filtrów. Bez okularów. Bez nakrycia głowy.

Panie - bez makijażu, w rozpuszczonych włosach tak, żeby widoczna była długość włosów

Panowie - dodatkowo zdjęcie z profilu

* **POKOJÓWKA**- kobieta ok. 30-40 lat. Stawka 180 zł gotówką po planie (przymiarki stacjonarne: 60 zł + 120 zł za dzień zdjęciowy). Przymiarki w piątek 10.10 na Chełmskiej po 14:00 

**13 PAŹDZIERNIKA (poniedziałek):**
* **GOŚCIE BARU / PRZECHODNIE - wiek ok. 20-55 lat. **Jedna scena, godziny popołudniowe.** **Stawka 120 zł gotówką po planie
* **STRAŻNICY GRANICZNI - mężczyźni ok. 30-50 lat**. Jedna scena. Poproszę wymiary w zgłoszeniu. Stawka 140 zł gotówką po planie
* **STRAŻNIK GRANICZNY Z OWCZARKIEM NIEMIECKIM **- jak wyżej. Jedna scena. Stawka 180 zł gotówką po planie.
* **KELNERKA **- **kobieta ok. 20-35 lat**.Jedna scena. Stawka 120 zł gotówką po planie

**14 PAŹDZIERNIKA (wtorek):**
* **KOBIETA NA SPACERZE Z PSEM** - wiek bez znaczenia. Psiak nie może być rasowy. Kundle będą najlepsze. Poproszę zdjęcie psa również. **Jedna scena nocna. 240 zł przelewem**

Ponieważ gramy lata 80te mamy nieuniknione wytyczne charakteryzacji:

**Dla wszystkich:**
* brak tatuaży w widocznych miejscach (ręce również, na nogach u pań też odpadają)
* bez tuneli w uszach
* kolczyki w nosie, brwiach czy wardze trzeba wyjąć na zdjęcia

**Panowie:**
* bez wygolonych boków i bez włosów ścinanych maszynką, bez zarostów od barbera
* długie włosy super
* łysi panowie niestety odpadają

**Panie:**
* paznokcie TYLKO naturalne. 
* bez permanentnych makijaży, doklejonych rzęs i innych ingerencji współczesnych kosmetologii

**ZGŁOSZENIA**

Poproszę na adres: **dominika@podtytulem.pl**

W tytule: **JB + wybrane daty**

W treści: imię i nazwisko, wiek, nr telefonu, miejscowość + wymiary: wzrost, klatka, pas, biodra, rozmiar ubrania i buta

W załączniku: ZDJĘCIE TWARZY I SYLWETKI: tylko z dnia zgłoszenia.

Portretowe selfie w dziennym świetle, na wprost, patrząc w obiektyw. Bez żadnych filtrów. Bez okularów. Bez nakrycia głowy.

Panie - bez makijażu, w rozpuszczonych włosach tak, żeby widoczna była długość włosów

Panowie - dodatkowo zdjęcie z profilu

Casting Call (Non-Union) for COUPLES/POLYCULES - Paid

Looking for actors to play the role of clients in a simulated therapy session. The video clips will be used in an online training system for counselors and psychologists. The sessions include some scripted elements to prepare, and then some improv with prompts.

We are currently interested in filming with mature couples, queer couples, interracial couples, or throuples/polycules of various gender identity combinations. All ages, all gender expressions/identities, all ethnicities, and persons with disabilities are welcome. 

All experience levels with acting are welcome, including experienced actors with less experienced partners. We are committed to making this a respectful and safe process, with open communication and respect for boundaries.

Comfortable English fluency is required.

Immediate filming dates are October 10 through 17, but more will occur in the future so please submit if you're interested at all.

Location is downtown Vancouver - Gastown. Pay is $90 CAD per performer, wit the expectation of some prepared material, duration: 1 hour

Please email phil@skillsetter.com with your headshot and resume. If you've submitted for a past session, you're welcome to submit again. We do sometimes receive more submissions than we are able to respond to, but we do read them all, and we do save your submissions for future consideration.

Każdy pomysł, każdy gest, każdy dźwięk – w naszym teatrze mogą stać się sztuką. Znajdź wśród nas swoje miejsce!🎭✨

Kogo szukamy?
🎤 Aktorów musicalowych – jeśli śpiewasz, tańczysz lub chcesz spróbować kombinacji tych dziedzin – to miejsce dla Ciebie! Nie musisz umieć wszystkiego, możesz zgłosić się tylko do śpiewu, tylko do tańca lub połączyć kilka umiejętności.

🎨 Artystycznych dusz – jeśli piszesz scenariusze (nawet te w głowie ;)), grasz na instrumencie, malujesz, tworzysz (w dowolnej formie) lub chcesz spróbować swoich sił jako:
- dźwiękowiec,
- oświetleniowiec,
- scenograf,
- choreograf,
- kostiumolog,
pokaż nam, co potrafisz, a my znajdziemy sposób, aby świat mógł to zobaczyć!

Jak dołączyć?
1️⃣ Wypełnij formularz zgłoszeniowy https://forms.gle/LtfDKg8cCCbjis1c8

2️⃣ Przygotuj prezentację swoich umiejętności - osobno lub w wybranej kombinacji:
* Śpiew: dwa dowolne utwory; plusem będą piosenki aktorskie lub musicalowe.
* Taniec: fragment choreografii min. 30 sekund (style Broadway Jazz, Modern Jazz, Contemporary, Fosse, Theatre, High Heels – dodatkowy atut!).
* Gra aktorska: fragment prozy lub wiersza; najlepiej po jednym z każdego 😉
* Kreatywność za kulisami: pokaż swoje prace, doświadczenie lub pomysły na żywo, na spotkaniu z nami!

💡 Nie musisz przygotowywać wszystkiego – pokaż to, co potrafisz najlepiej. Jeśli śpiewasz, przygotuj tylko śpiew; jeśli tańczysz, pokaż taniec; jeśli chcesz połączyć te umiejętności – super! Najważniejsze, abyśmy zobaczyli Twój talent i pasję.

3️⃣ Przyjdź na casting w poniedziałek, 20.10.2025 – więcej szczegółów otrzymasz mailem po wysłaniu formularza.

Dlaczego warto?
* Jesteśmy projektem non-profit – robimy to z pasji i miłości do teatru!
* Wielka szansa na rozwój talentu, zdobycie doświadczenia i poznanie wspaniałej, twórczej społeczności ❤

🎬 Nie czekaj! Kliknij tutaj, aby zgłosić się i znaleźć swoje miejsce w naszej artystycznej ekipie!

Nie czekaj, bo kurtyna już idzie w górę…

🔗 Link do formularza zgłoszeniowego: https://forms.gle/LtfDKg8cCCbjis1c8

items.text:
Du hast Lust auf kreative Rollen, schnelle Szenen und pointierten Humor?  

Dann könnte das hier genau dein Ding sein:

Ich starte ein neues Comedy-Projekt auf TikTok, YouTube & Co.  

Geplant sind kurze POV-Sketche, Beziehungsszenen, Alltagssatire und emotionale Mini-Dramen – alles mit einem Augenzwinkern und klarer Rollenstruktur.

Drehort ist Berlin.

Was ich suche:

- Schauspielerin im Alter von 28 bis 44 Jahren  

- Spaß an geskripteten Szenen und klaren Rollenbildern  

- Offen für verschiedene Rollen (z. B. Freundin, Kollegin, Date, Affäre, Nachbarin etc.)  

- Gefühl für Timing, Mimik und Punchlines  

- Keine Angst vor Kamera, Humor oder Drama

Was dich erwartet:

- Kreative Zusammenarbeit mit einem Creator, der Storytelling & Timing liebt  

- Szenen mit klarer Struktur, aber Raum für eigene Ideen  

- Möglichkeit, dich als wiederkehrende Figur zu etablieren  

- Hinweis zur Vergütung: Das Projekt befindet sich aktuell in der Aufbauphase und wird zunächst ohne feste Bezahlung umgesetzt. Ziel ist es, gemeinsam etwas Starkes aufzubauen – mit Credits in jedem Clip und der Option auf langfristige Zusammenarbeit, sobald das Projekt wächst.

Interesse?  

Dann schreib mir direkt hier oder per Mail an Dennis.Laubert@Web.de.

Gerne mit kurzem Video, Link zu deinem Profil oder einfach ein paar Zeilen zu dir.

Liebe Grüße, 

Dennis Laubert

items.text:
**CASTING VIDEO – MANN UM DIE 40 – HANDWERKSBIER**
## 

Sind Sie ein Mann um die 40, natürlich und kamerafreundlich?

Sie sprechen **fließend Deutsch** (Pflicht) und können sich mit unserem Team auf **Französisch oder Englisch**verständigen?

Wir suchen einen Darsteller für einen Werbedreh zur Erstellung von **Videoinhalten für die sozialen Netzwerke** einer **handwerklich gebrauten Biermarke**.

📍 **Ort**: Lausanne, Schweiz

🕐 **Dauer**: Halber Drehtag

📅 **Datum**: Wochenende **16.–17. Oktober 2025**

💰 **Vergütung**: 100 € 

👉 **Bewerbung bitte mit**:

📸 Ein paar **aktuelle Fotos**

🎤 Einem kurzen **Vorstellungsvideo** (ca. 30 Sekunden) auf Deutsch

📩 **Bewerbungen und Fragen** bitte per Privatnachricht

## **CASTING VIDÉO – HOMME QUARANTAINE – BIÈRE ARTISANALE**

Vous êtes un homme d’une quarantaine d’années, naturel et à l’aise devant la caméra ?

Vous parlez **allemand couramment** (impératif), et vous pouvez communiquer en **français ou en anglais** avec nos équipes ?

Nous recherchons un figurant pour un tournage publicitaire destiné à la création de **contenus vidéos pour les réseaux sociaux** d’une **marque de bière artisanale**.

📍 **Lieu** : Lausanne, Suisse

🕐 **Durée** : 1 demi-journée de tournage

📅 **Date** : week-end du **16-17 octobre 2025**

💰 **Rémunération** : 100 € 

👉 **Pour candidater, merci d’envoyer** :

📸 Quelques **photos récentes**

🎤 Une courte **vidéo de présentation** (30 sec environ) en allemand

📩 **Candidatures et questions** par message privé

## 
## **VIDEO CASTING – MAN IN HIS 40s – CRAFT BEER**

Are you a man in your 40s, natural and comfortable on camera?

Do you speak **fluent German** (mandatory) and can communicate with our team in **French or English**?

We are looking for a background actor for a commercial shoot to create **video content for the social media channels** of a **craft beer brand**.

📍 **Location**: Lausanne, Switzerland

🕐 **Duration**: Half-day shoot

📅 **Date**: Weekend of **October 16–17, 2025**

💰 **Compensation**: 100 €

👉 **To apply, please send**:

📸 A few **recent photos**

🎤 A short **introduction video** (around 30 seconds) in German

📩 **Applications and questions** via private message

items.text:
TENNESSEE WILLIAMS MONOLOGUES | LISTENING SESSION

Online | Free

Hi Everyone,

On **Monday evening October 13, 7-8:30pm Eastern**, I'll present this free online session. This is a series of mostly-Tennessee Williams based free class sessions, at the end of which we will also talk about the upcoming January Clarksdale Workshops: Acting and Playwriting sessions in Tennessee Williams' Mississippi Delta (Jan 4-10), taught by me and playwright Lucy Thurber and director Jenna Worsham.

On Monday we'll listen to 8-9 monologues I'll select from Tennessee Williams characters that are less known than his most famous ones. It's amazing to hear the variety in his writing. This is part of a project I'm working on that I'll tell you more about that night. When you reserve, let me know if you want to read. It's also fine to just come and listen.

Join us!

**TO RESERVE:** email **classes@monologueaudition.com**

*****can't do this one? email classes@monologueaudition.com to hear about the next ones*****

Karen

**KAREN KOHLHAAS** is an Atlantic Theater Company founding member, director, and senior teacher. She is a master teacher of Practical Aesthetic acting technique, and teaches acting, directing, monologues and cold reading, online, in New York City, in Clarksdale, Mississippi and around the US. She is a Tennessee Williams scholar and curator of the Tennessee Williams Rectory Museum, and is editing a documentary series about Williams' time in the Mississippi Delta. The Clarksdale Workshops are residentail week-long trainings for actors and playwrights (Williams scene study and playwriting in January), and for actors and teachers (Monologue Audition training in August). For more information on classes please visit art-and-audition.com, and TennWmsDelta.com.

sharedPost.text:
Casting Call

Production: Mother's Ruin, by Steve Bird (Back by popular demand!)

The story so far in the life of Liverpool comedian Garry Skyner, one of Britain's first- born victims of the Thalidomide medical disaster. Steve Birds play is a moving and emotional, yet hard hitting play about the highs, lows, struggles and sheer determination of a loving Mother and her son who refused to be beaten by the Government and company that profited from this medical disaster.

We are looking for a talented female actor playing range 20-30ys, who is from Liverpool or can do a convincing accent, for the lead role of Frances, Gary's Mum.
Frances is a spirited, humourous woman, who whilst having a heart of gold, has an inner strength, is tough, and fights for her child and what is right.
If you believe you are what we are looking for please send you CV and headshot to elainestewart46@yahoo.com 

Auditions to take place on Sunday 21st September 1pm-3pm at a Liverpool venue to be disclosed on receipt of CV, and a script will be provided. 

Performances will take place at the Epstein Theatre on 27th and 28th February 2026.

You must be available for rehearsals Sundays 1pm- 4pm (in Liverpool) starting 2nd November.
*This is a profit share production

items.text:
We are now casting for our Halloween Party show .

The show will tour into community based venues, Nursing and Residential Homes, Day Centres.

We are seeking self-contained experienced hardworking singer/ performers who are keen to take quality musical shows to the community.

The Dates

Rehearsals –17th and 18th October in London

Playing Dates-20th -31st October-

We work Monday to Friday only.

The show is a one man/woman show so we are looking for experienced engaging performers with great singing voices,

We are looking for drivers with cars only

Please confirm where you are based in your application.

We offer £700 per week plus fuel on the road .

We are also casting our one man / woman musical show Winter Wonderland that will tour care homes and community based throughout December.

The show is production style show based on songs from the musicals Mary Poppins, White Christmas, Singing In The Rain, The Wizard Of Oz As well as traditional Christmas songs and carols, comedy routines and festive entertainment for all.

Dates

Rehearsals 24th -28th November

Playing dates 1st-23rd December

We perform two 60 minute shows 6 days a week.

We are offering 600 .00 per week fuel on the road and accommodation allowance when required.

MUST BE A DRIVER WITH A CAR

Please email details including a singing reel to

info@theentertainmentproviders.co.uk

items.text:
Hi everyone! I'm casting 'All-Round Champion', a CSA & Emmy Award-winning reality sports competition series that brings together 10 of the best youth athletes from across North America and the UK. items.text:
CHRISTMAS CASTING CALL – ENSEMBLE CAST and GROTTO ELVES

 

Seeking talented performers for this year’s production of The Magical Christmas Adventure — a multi-award-winning live performance and immersive attraction based near Newbury, Berkshire. The production combines the best of pantomime with interactive entertainment, inviting audiences to become part of the story.

With an all-new show for 2025, we are casting for principal roles to join our cast. Each tour runs for approximately 2 hours, with groups departing every 10 minutes — up to 48 tours per day.

 

Salary:

£15.00 hourly rate

Accommodation will be included

Breakfast, Lunch & Dinner are all provided for you.

 

Location: Headley, Berkshire

Dates:

Rehearsal from 18th November

Soft Launch 22th November

1st full performance day 23rd December

Last performance day 24th December

Approx 22 days in total

 

ROLES:

 

GRAND MASTER TOY MAKER

Santa's most trusted elf and the head of toy production at the North Pole.

 

SNOWFLAKE

In charge of keeping all the snowballs at the Ice Castle ready for battle whenever needed.

 

SPARKLE

A friendly, bubbly, energetic, and knowledgeable elf who welcomes guests to the North Pole.

 

GROTTO ELF

You'll be a bubbly, charismatic personality meeting families to take them to and stay with them doing their meeting with Santa.

 

If you would like to join us on this magical adventure, please email your CV, headshot and covering letter to [mike@themagicalchristmasadventure.co.uk](mailto:mike@themagicalchristmasadventure.co.uk)

 

[www.themagicalchristmasadventure.co.uk](http://www.themagicalchristmasadventure.co.uk)

With ONLY 2 WEEKS LEFT, make sure you’ve got your tickets as the countdown has begun for our highly anticipated Actors and Filmmakers Networking Event on Sunday, October 26th! Are you ready to take a transformative step in your career? This is your moment!

 

For years, Marble Academy has proudly facilitated these events. Following the incredible turnout at our June gathering, which drew over 90 attendees, we hope to build on this success. Just imagine the possibilities!

 

Get ready to immerse yourself in a space filled with talented actors, visionary directors, influential producers, and skilled crew members, all eager to share insights and forge meaningful connections. This is your chance to meet the kind of people who could help bring your next big project to life.

 

We’re also thrilled to announce that the talented Lisa Barton from Lisa Barton photography will be joining us at the event to showcase her stunning work. If you’re in need of captivating headshots, looking to refresh your current images, or simply aiming to elevate your professional presence, this is the perfect moment to make it happen.

 

Mark your calendars for Sunday, October 26th, from 2 PM to 6:30 PM at HOME Mcr, located at 2 Tony Wilson Place, Manchester, M15 4FN.

 

🎟️ Secure your ticket now and be part of something special: [https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/actors-and-filmmakers-networking-event-tickets-1509159349239](https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/actors-and-filmmakers-networking-event-tickets-1509159349239) 

I can’t wait to see you there

items.text:
**RE:SCULPT – Instructor Auditions | London**

** **

**Think you’ve got the fire to lead from the front?**

We’re on the hunt for instructors who bring serious energy, bold vibes, and unstoppable presence to every RE:SCULPT class. This is your chance to join a brand that’s shaking up the fitness industry and setting new standards for what a reformer-inspired strength workout can be.

At RE:SCULPT, we don’t just teach classes - we *create experiences.* You’ll need to lift the room, command the energy, and connect with clients through every beat and every move. You’ll coach with precision, motivate with purpose, and deliver a workout that keeps clients coming back for more.

 

We’re looking for instructors who:
* Have undeniable stage presence and confidence on the mic.
* Understand how to blend performance with purpose - ensuring every workout has a vibe and is technically strong.
* Can create awesome energy while maintaining control and flow with the beat of the music.
* Can embrace the RE:SCULPT brand, values and community.

In return, we offer industry-leading training in the RE:SCULPT method, ongoing coaching development, and the opportunity to be part of our first **London** studio launch near **Battersea.**

Auditions are coming soon - and trust us, spots are limited.
High standards. Huge opportunity.

 

Is this for you?

Email your CV, highlighting relevant qualifications and experience, to headcoach@resculptstudios.co.uk

 
* *YOU NEED A MINIMUM OF A LEVEL 2 FITNESS QUALIFICATION, OR A PROFESSIONAL DANCE BACKGROUND.*
* *A PILATES QUALIFICATION IS NOT REQUIRED.*
* *AVAILABILITY FOR AT LEAST 2 “BLOCKS” OF CLASSES PER WEEK*

A, i Polsat nie beceluję mi nic za product placement.
Ja to z serca robię.

▪️ eleganckich MĘŻCZYZN do małych epizodów kontynuacyjnych (27.10)

Wyjazd godz. 5 z centrum lub dojazd własny na godz. 7 (Antoninów). Plan ma nie być całodniowy. Stawka dla statystów 140zł gotówką po planie, dla epizodów 400zł gotówką po drugim dniu zdjęciowym. 

Zgłoszenia wraz z imieniem i nazwiskiem, numerem telefonu, AKTUALNYMI zdjęciami (sylwetka, twarz), przyjmujemy na adres: CASTING@ONSETAGENCY.PL w tytule wpisując „CMENTARZ”.

ISO the Canadian Jennifer Lopez 

N**on-union LatinX** female lead for our next vertical drama.

Project - When Time Brings Us Together

Director - Sid Zanforlin

Dates - Oct 21st- Oct 29th (7 days in that time frame)

Rate - $350/day

Production Company - Ottawood Film

Location - Richmond Hill

Flights and accommodations will be covered for actors travelling from outside Toronto.

**Storyline**

Kindhearted and beautiful factory worker Diane Brooker enters a marriage of convenience with powerful CEO Steve Fulcher, only to be separated by tragedy and memory loss. A year later, fate brings them back together. Sparking a journey of rediscovery, romance, and Diane’s transformation from a humiliated outcast to a confident woman who reclaims her dignity and love.

**Diane Gomez 45-years-old**

A single LatinX mom that would do anything for her 20ish son. When younger she was a dancer and could charm anyone but has recently lost her confidence.

Please submit a head shot and resume to ottawoodcasting@gmail.com

Jigsaw Casting is looking for a George Washington lookalike in their mid 60’s for a Software Campaign across North America! 

We’re looking for MEN mid 60’s+ who bear an uncanny resemblance to George Washington. Have you ever been mistaken for the first president of the United States? Do you think you might be mistaken for good old G.W. if someone put the right kind of wig on you? If yes, this is for you!

No acting experience required, just a willingness to play along.

This shoots in Toronto, Canada if someone lives far from this location, travel and accommodation will be provided. 

IF YOU KNOW OF SOMEONE, PLEASE PASS THIS ON!

Compensation if selected: $6,675.00. CAD. Buyout is based on survival of the edit and includes all lifts, edits, versions. This is a non union job.

Must be available for these Important dates:

Recall: Saturday Oct 18th - 21st Via Zoom if you live far. In person if you are in Toronto.
Travel Days (for those who do not live in Toronto and has to fly in): Travel to Toronto Oct 27, Travel Home Oct 31 TBD
Wardrobe: Oct 27 and or 28th TBD (in Toronto)
Shoot Date: Oct 29 or Oct 30 - TBD Which day needed (in Toronto)

DEADLINE TO SUBMIT: ASAP OR BEFORE FRIDAY OCTOBER 17, 2025 AT 6PM. EST.

Submission Link: https://aircastle.ca/submit/g-dub

items.text:
**CASTING CALL – Male Actor (35–45) for Paid Ad Video ($100 / 2–3 Hours)**

**Company:** LAS Bespoke – Premium Automotive Detailing & Protection (Surrey, BC)
**Contact:** luxuryautospa.van@gmail.com
**Union Status:** Non-Union
**Shoot Location:** Surrey, BC
**Shoot Date:** Flexible between October 14–18 (Exact day confirmed with actor)
**Time Commitment:** 2–3 hours
**Pay Rate:** $100 flat

**Project Description:**
We’re filming a short advertisement video for LAS Bespoke, a premium automotive brand known for ceramic coatings and paint protection. The video will feature you wearing our branded merch and delivering short, confident lines on camera. The ad will be used for social media and digital marketing.

**Character Breakdown:**
• **Male (Caucasian)**
• **Age:** 35–45
• **Look:** Clean-cut, friendly, confident, and trustworthy appearance
• **Personality:** Comfortable speaking naturally to camera, clear voice, good posture, and strong presence
• **Experience:** Previous on-camera or commercial experience preferred but not required

**Requirements:**
• Must be comfortable being filmed and following short scripts
• Must be reliable, punctual, and presentable
• Will be provided branded clothing for the shoot

**To Apply:**
Email **luxuryautospa.van@gmail.com** with the subject line **“Ad Casting – Vancouver”** and include:
• 2–3 recent photos or headshots
• A short intro video or link to any previous work (if available)
• Your availability between **October 14–18**

We’ll contact selected candidates directly to confirm date and time.

topComments.text: That's A LOT to ask for a measly $100. "Premium" business paying chips for ad creation.
Well, I wouldn’t mind 100 bucks isn’t much but if they could also give my truck a ceramic coating, I’d go for it

Hi everyone! 🫶🏻

I’m Bogi, Casting Manager at Deep Creative Collective (https://www.tiktok.com/@thedeepcc) based in Budapest. We create fun and viral content for brands on TikTok, Instagram, and Google.

Right now, I’m looking for someone in Zagreb who could be the next host for Wolt’s video ads! 🎥
We’re searching for someone energetic, passionate and confident, who would love to appear on camera and represent cool brands.

Details:
 • Location: Zagreb
 • Work: 1 shoot day/month (6–8 hours)
 • Content: 6 short videos per month
 • Pay: 120€ per shoot day
 • Requirements: 18-30years old MAN good English & ability to ride a bike 🚲

If this sounds like you (or someone you know), feel free to reach out – I’d love to hear from you! ✨

sharedPost.text:
Film zostanie wysłany na ogolnolicealny Fresh Form film festiwal, sa dwie reżyserki, w tym ja, z małym doświadczeniem ale wielkim zapałem. Mamy kamerę i stroje. Nie jest to płatne, można powiedzieć hobbistyczne, ale na pewno będzie to ciekawa przygoda. Okolice Warszawy, Piaseczna. Dni nagrywek są elastyczne 

Film jest obyczajowy, opowiada o grupie nastolatków zmagających się z problemami w rodzinie, z używkami i chorobą. Film opiera się na scenach rozmów, drogi i ‚gonitwy’. jest bardzo emocjonalny i pełen pasji.

Fajnie jakby zgłoszeni mieli styl bliski alternatywnemu, rockowemu (wielkim plusem byłaby umiejętność gry na gitarze) Szukamy przede wszystkim chłopaka 170-190cm z kręconymi włosami, grający rolę najlepszego przyjaciela głównego bohatera który stara się pomóc w leczeniu jego matki.

Poboczne role to postać chłopaka o podobnym wzroście, jasne proste lub falowane włosy, oraz jeszcze dwójki chłopaków, bez większych wymagań (jeden lepiej by było jakby miał długie włosy, hipisowski styl)

Naprawdę doceniam każdego chętnego, jesteśmy bardzo zaangażowane w tworzenie, a scenariusz jest naprawdę ambitny.

items.text:
🎬 **Casting-Aufruf: Schauspieler & Statisten (m/w/d) für Werbespot gesucht**

Hey zusammen 👋

Für den Dreh eines kurzen, professionellen **Werbevideos** suchen wir **2 Schauspieler und 1–2 Statisten**, die Lust haben, Teil einer modernen Business-Produktion zu sein.

⏰ **Dauer:** ca. 3–4 Stunden
💶 **Aufwandsentschädigung:** nach Absprache

🎥 **Was dich erwartet:**
Ein kleiner Dreh in entspannter Atmosphäre, mit klarer Szene und einfachem Dialog.
Keine Vorbereitung nötig – Hauptsache, du bist zuverlässig, natürlich und hast Spaß vor der Kamera.

📩 **Interesse?**
Schick mir einfach eine kurze Nachricht mit:
* Einem aktuellen Foto
* Ein paar Worten zu dir
* Deiner Verfügbarkeit am Drehtag

Ich freu mich auf euch!

topComments.text:
Es muß schon erwähnt werden, wo es stattfindet und wann. 
Ansonsten erscheint es unglaubwürdig.

items.text:
Actors (non-union) needed for a documentary regarding Elizabeth Johnson Jr who was the last convicted witch to be exonerated from the 1692 Salem Witchcraft Trials.

The ideal actor for Elizabeth will have strawberry blond or slight red hair, be of average height and able to portray early 20s.

Two additional actors will be needed as elders (40-60) who arrest her and walk her away.

The shoot will require one day in early November or early December on north of Boston. Pay will be negotiated.  Access to a late 17th century costume is a plus. Send headshot, resume and November, December availability to SalemHistoricalTours@gmail.com

items.text:
Do you have a passion for all things scary?

A walk that sends shivers down spines?

Or maybe you just love being part of the chaos behind the scares?

Fear Columbus in Columbus, Ohio is HIRING IMMEDIATELY for:

🩸 Haunted House Actors (unleash your inner monster, clown, or demon)

🩸 Event Staff (keep the terror running smoothly from the shadows)

✨ No experience? No problem. We’ll train you to scare like a pro.

✨ evening shifts + the most fun job you’ll ever have.

✨ Be part of one of the largest haunted attractions in Ohio.

This is your chance to join our spooky family and create memories (and nightmares) that guests won’t forget!

💀 Apply NOW and come be a part of all the spooky fun! 

⚡ Don’t wait — the screams start soon and spots are filling FAST! 

Click the link below or in my bio for info on what it entails working here and for the application! 

Can't wait to see you <3

[https://fearcolumbus.com/applications/](https://fearcolumbus.com/applications/)

**Statister søges (ulønnet)**

Hej alle, 

Vi søger 3 statister til vores kortfilm FLYT DIG i alderen 60-100, køn er underordnet. 

**LOGLINE**

En konfliktsky ung mand bliver udnyttet af sine venner og ignoreret af sin familie. Da hans rebelske fætter hjælper ham med at flytte, må han indse, at frihed ikke bare handler om at bryde ud – men om at turde definere sine egne grænser.

Optagelserne foregår i tilst tirsdag d. 14 oktober fra 9-17. Der vil være forplejninger på set.

Skriv til mig på messenger eller til *sara774g@gmail.com* ved interesse.

Venlig Hilsen, Sara Riahi

*FUNDET! 

Jeg søger en hundeejer med en sød familiehund (golden retriever, labrador, den slags, gerne i en lys farve) der kunne have lyst til at have deres hund med i nogle reklamebilleder/film der fremhæver sommerhushygge i Blokhus 😊🦮📷 

Vi laver nemlig nogle optagelser i Blokhus mandag-onsdag, hvor vi gerne vil have nogle scener med en hund. Det drejer sig om et par timer, gerne tirsdag eftermiddag, men andre tidspunkter er også mulige, og det er kun hunden der skal være med. Hunden skal agere sammen med en skuespilsfamilie. 
**Vi har 1500kr til betaling for dette.**

Skriv gerne en kommentar, send mig en besked eller mail på daniel@24copenhagen.dk, hvis du er interesseret.

God søndag!

items.text:
**CASTING CALL – LONDON (November–December)**

Hi Everyone,

I’m Ben, a founder trying to do something a bit mad in the run-up to Christmas.

I’ve made a new family game and have **5,000 boxes to sell before Christmas**… or I have to be a normal adult and go back to being an accountant again! 

We’re filming the real journey: street pitches, rejections, laughs, and small wins, all turned into short daily LinkedIn episodes (1–3 minutes each). Think *founder documentary meets chaos comedy*.

I’m looking for a few actors to jump in and help out, people who can play along naturally as friends, supporters, or street crew in different moments of the campaign.

**Location:** London

**When:** November–December (run-up to Christmas)

**Paid freelance role:** Not a massive budget, but there is a budget.

**Commitment:** Half a day, 1 day a week for 4 weeks. Need 5 actors, one for each day of the week.

**Who suits this:**
* Chatty, funny, naturally comfortable on camera
* Up for improvising and rolling with the madness
* Down-to-earth, good energy, friendly vibe

If you’re **fun, talented, and up for helping make a tabletop game go viral**, drop me a DM with a short intro or clip.

Ben

🎭 FREE DRAMA WORKSHOP for young people in MANCHESTER this NOVEMBER 🎭

Join us at Red Players Academy for the FREE LAUNCH WORKSHOP of our BRAND NEW SATURDAY CLASSES at our well-established and highly-reputable drama school for young performers aged 9+

🌐 www.redplayersacademy.com/courses

🔴 RPA is Manchester’s premier drama school and talent agency – known for combining cutting-edge academic research with professional industry experience! Whether you’re just starting out or already a working actor, our workshops are tailored to support every level!

🔴 We are an elite training provider, offering advanced workshops in Acting, Drama, Movement, and Contemporary Performance. We teach all aspects of acting for both stage and screen, and are specialists in innovative Creative Practice!

🎬 Our students are currently appearing in:

📺 Netflix’s Adolescence
⚽ CBBC’s Jamie Johnson FC
🎭 13 Going on 30 @ Manchester Opera House
🔍 CBBC’s Odd Squad
…and more!

What you can expect at RPA:

🗓️ Weekly Saturday Drama Classes in Altrincham
🎭 Opportunities to participate in an end-of-year Showcase at a local theatre
🎬 Acting and Performance Workshops for Stage & Screen
🎓 Taught by qualified practitioners with professional industry experience 
🌟 Curriculum designed by Acting Coach & Performance Academic Lee Battle – credits include Coronation Street, Casualty, the BAFTA winning BBC drama The Street, Robin Hood, Awaydays and many more
📣 To be considered to join our SPOTLIGHT-registered Young Performers Talent Agency
🎬 Project-based, intensive, industry-focused practical learning environment

🗓️ LAUNCHING SATURDAY 1st NOVEMBER 2025

📍Limited spaces available – sign up to your FREE introductory workshop now!

📱 07441 396970
📧 info@redplayers.co.uk

items.summary:
🎭 FREE DRAMA WORKSHOP for young people in MANCHESTER this NOVEMBER 🎭

Join us at Red Players Academy for the FREE LAUNCH WORKSHOP of our BRAND NEW SATURDAY CLASSES at our well-established and highly-reputable drama school for young performers aged 9+

🌐 www.redplayersacademy.com/courses

🔴 RPA is Manchester’s premier drama school and talent agency – known for combining cutting-edge academic research with professional industry experience! Whether you’re just starting out or already a working actor, our workshops are tailored to support every level!

🔴 We are an elite training provider, offering advanced workshops in Acting, Drama, Movement, and Contemporary Performance. We teach all aspects of acting for both stage and screen, and are specialists in innovative Creative Practice!

🎬 Our students are currently appearing in:

📺 Netflix’s Adolescence
⚽ CBBC’s Jamie Johnson FC
🎭 13 Going on 30 @ Manchester Opera House
🔍 CBBC’s Odd Squad
…and more!

What you can expect at RPA:

🗓️ Weekly Saturday Drama Classes in Altrincham
🎭 Opportunities to participate in an end-of-year Showcase at a local theatre
🎬 Acting and Performance Workshops for Stage & Screen
🎓 Taught by qualified practitioners with professional industry experience 
🌟 Curriculum designed by Acting Coach & Performance Academic Lee Battle – credits include Coronation Street, Casualty, the BAFTA winning BBC drama The Street, Robin Hood, Awaydays and many more
📣 To be considered to join our SPOTLIGHT-registered Young Performers Talent Agency
🎬 Project-based, intensive, industry-focused practical learning environment

🗓️ LAUNCHING SATURDAY 1st NOVEMBER 2025

📍Limited spaces available – sign up to your FREE introductory workshop now!

📱 07441 396970
📧 info@redplayers.co.uk
🌐 www.redplayersacademy.com

Seeking 10 actors of all backgrounds for the creation of a short simple experimental film this Saturday 11th October 10am-12.30pm. The film involves simply looking into the camera for half an hour or so responding to various prompts. 

Filming will take place in my studio in Bermondsey, London SE1. please email me with interest angelzinovieff@gmail.com

This is unpaid, but I will provide refreshments!

items.text:
TENNESSEE WILLIAMS MONOLOGUES | LISTENING SESSION

Online | Free

Hi Everyone,

On **Monday evening October 13, 7-8:30pm Eastern**, I'll present this free online session. This is a series of mostly-Tennessee Williams based free class sessions, at the end of which we will also talk about the upcoming January Clarksdale Workshops: Acting and Playwriting sessions in Tennessee Williams' Mississippi Delta (Jan 4-10), taught by me and playwright Lucy Thurber and director Jenna Worsham.

On Monday we'll listen to 8-9 monologues I'll select from Tennessee Williams characters that are less known than his most famous ones. It's amazing to hear the variety in his writing. This is part of a project I'm working on that I'll tell you more about that night. When you reserve, let me know if you want to read. It's also fine to just come and listen.

Join us!

**TO RESERVE:** email **classes@monologueaudition.com**

*****can't do this one? email classes@monologueaudition.com to hear about the next ones*****

Karen

**KAREN KOHLHAAS** is an Atlantic Theater Company founding member, director, and senior teacher. She is a master teacher of Practical Aesthetic acting technique, and teaches acting, directing, monologues and cold reading, online, in New York City, in Clarksdale, Mississippi and around the US. She is a Tennessee Williams scholar and curator of the Tennessee Williams Rectory Museum, and is editing a documentary series about Williams' time in the Mississippi Delta. The Clarksdale Workshops are residentail week-long trainings for actors and playwrights (Williams scene study and playwriting in January), and for actors and teachers (Monologue Audition training in August). For more information on classes please visit art-and-audition.com, and TennWmsDelta.com.

Don’t forget to grab your tickets! 50% sold out!

Georgetown Little Theatre proudly presents A Telling of The Christmas Carol — running November 27th to December 6th, 2025.

This isn’t your average Christmas Carol… it’s a witty, fast-paced, and heartfelt reimagining of the holiday classic. Ebenezer Scrooge still faces ghosts, regrets, and redemption, but along the way you’ll be treated to:
Laugh-out-loud comedy
Ghosts who bicker like overworked employees
Marley fumbling through haunting “protocols”
And the timeless spirit of generosity and hope

You might laugh, you might cry — but one thing is certain: you’ll have a fantastic time!

✨ 50% sold out already — don’t wait! ✨

[https://app.arts-people.com/index.php?show=279396](https://app.arts-people.com/index.php?show=279396)

items.text:
Are you and your family ready to be TV stars? 🎉

I’m beyond excited to share that I’ve teamed up as the official connector between families and Fox casting producer Tom Burkhardt for the hit game show, “The Quiz With Balls,” hosted by Jay Pharoah! If your crew is high-energy, competitive, and ready for an adventure, this is your chance to compete in Belgium next February for life-changing prizes and unforgettable memories—broadcast on Fox!

I’m not just passing along the info—I’ll support you every step of the way. I’ll walk you through the process, help you prep for auditions, and even feature your family on my podcast for a little extra spotlight! 🌟

Want to learn more or get started? Message me here on Facebook or email yolandanollie@gmail.com for details, tips, or to set up a pre-audition chat. Ready to apply right now?

Click the link: [quiz.castingcrane.com/age-gateand](https://quiz.castingcrane.com/age-gateand) mention “ @Tom Burkhardt and Yolanda Nollie” as your referral.

Let’s make your family the next big thing on TV—reach out today!

#castingcalls #GameShowFun #familyadventures #TheQuizWithBalls #FoxTv #TVOpportunity #PodcastFeature

Are you and your family ready to be TV stars? 🎉

I’m beyond excited to share that I’ve teamed up as the official connector between families and Fox casting producer Tom Burkhardt for the hit game show, “The Quiz With Balls,” hosted by Jay Pharoah! If your crew is high-energy, competitive, and ready for an adventure, this is your chance to compete in Belgium next February for life-changing prizes and unforgettable memories—broadcast on Fox!

I’m not just passing along the info—I’ll support you every step of the way. I’ll walk you through the process, help you prep for auditions, and even feature your family on my podcast for a little extra spotlight! 🌟

Want to learn more or get started? Message me here on Facebook or email yolandanollie@gmail.com for details, tips, or to set up a pre-audition chat. Ready to apply right now?

items.text:
**SHORT FILM CREW CALL -***** Beyond the Blue Light***

*ISO of lgbtq, bipoc, and immigrant filmmakers to fill the following positions. All details below. Students welcome!*

*PAID:*

Studio Teacher (one minor 8 or 9 years old)

*IMDB Credit, Copy, Meals, Gas Stipend:*

2nd AC

Key Grip 

G&E Swing

Costumer (+ materials stipend)

Boom OP

PA

**Synopsis:**

*Beyond the Blue Light* is an emotionally charged drama about the cost of apathy in the chronically online era told through the perspective of two trans latine immigrants. 

**Location:**

Los Angeles: Hollywood & North Hollywood

**Dates:**

11/1 - 11/4

**About the Director:**

Simone Brazzini is an award winning filmmaker from Lima, Peru and now based in Los Angeles. Their debut LA short will be making its world premiere at the Micheaux Film Festival. They were recently named in a Deadline article and is a Soho House x Creative Futures Mentee. Simone founded Vibes Video in 2021, a production company that creates radically authentic work across all genres with a focus on lgbtq, bipoc, and neurodiverse voices on and off camera. 

**To Submit:**

Please email a portfolio and/or resume to vibesvideoproductions@gmail.com AND CC productions.fakeid@gmail.com

**THANK YOU**

Studies show women are less likely to survive cardiac arrest than men, primarily because they are less likely to receive bystander CPR.

Learning how to save someone's live with a fully certificated and accredited course can take just 3 hours, learn how to do CPR, use and AED and how to be the person to save some grandmother, mother, daughter or aunty, be there reason someone else makes it home alive!

items.text:
My name is Luke Kenyon, and I’m a film student at SAE Liverpool. We’re currently working on a new short film project titled Last Night and are looking to cast two male-identifying actors (mid twenties)to join our team. This project is Non paid but we will be providing travel expenses as well as catering 

Shooting dates 9th - 15th November 2025 Liverpool, England

Synopsis -

On the anniversary of his best friend’s suicide, Aaron plans to end his own life. He ignores his mothers phone calls and edges closer towards his own end, until he unexpectedly hears a knock at his apartment front door. His best friend, Ben, appears in an attempt to make amends and guide Aaron away from darkness. This intimate drama, through one final, raw conversation, forces Aaron to choose between following the same path that Ben took a year ago, or answering the call that could save him.

Aaron:

Aaron, mid 20's, slightly introverted and reserved. A complicated character with a lot going on in his mind. His low confidence makes it hard for him to open up to others about his feelings, especially about the loss of his best friend (Ben), who meant the world to him. He loves music and even used to play in a band with Ben. 

Ben:

Ben, mid 20's, soft and sensitive personality. His battles with his own mental health has led him to an unfortunate end, which ultimately, has hurt someone very close to him (Aaron), although this was never his intention. Ben’s aim is to make some sort of amends from his past actions and to help Aaron not make the same mistake that he did. 

If you have any questions about the project or roles, please don’t hesitate to get in touch — I’m happy to provide more information.

If you  are interested in applying, please use one of the provided links below or alternatively email me at 120206uk@saeinstitute.edu with your details, previous work, or portfolio. (Including heat shots) please provide which role you are applying for 

Thank you very much for your time We look forward to hearing from you!

Kind regards,

Luke Kenyon

Film Student, SAE Institute

https://www.backstage.com/casting/last-night-student-film-3019197/

https://www.starnow.com/casting/last-night-3021254/

https://www.mandy.com/aa/project/3021242/last-night/

items.text:
Rainhill Garrick Society are performing ‘ Habeus Corpus’ by Alan Bennett on February 12th-14th 2026.

Alan Bennett’s Habeus Corpus is set some time in the Seventies and follows the lives of the Wicksteed family. The story follows Dr and Muriel Wicksteed as they both seek pleasure and fun outside of their marital relationship. The farcical play is very fast paced, incredibly funny and occasionally surreal. The bumbling sex-obsessed British characters such as the virginal vicar, the ﬂat chested spinster, the peering doctor, his frustrated wife and of course a bra salesman man all come together in this bizarre and thoroughly entertaining story.

Parts available:-

Dennis Wicksteed - the hypochondriac son of Dr Wickseed, (20-30)

Felicity Rumpers - young, nubile, upper class  (20-30)

Constance Wicksteed - the sister of Dr Wicksteed, flat chested and sex starved, (20+) 

Sir Percy Shorter - chairman of the BMA, quite upper class and not too tall (Mid 40s+

Play read through Tuesday 21st October at 7.30 in Rainhill Village Hall

Auditions- Thursday 23rd October at 7.30 Rainhill Village Hall 

Rehearsals are on Tuesdays and Thursday evenings 7.30-9.30 and the 3 Sundays prior to the performance.

Audition pieces are available on request. 

We are an amateur group so the roles are unpaid, but we are a well respected group of 83 years standing who enjoy great support from a large dedicated audience. 

The play is great fun with some slapstick and music but with some poignant moments that say a lot about relationships.

For further information, contact: sophiebrogan99@gmail.com

·       Paser (44) - notowany recydywista, nie dbający jakoś przesadnie o wygląd czy kondycję fizyczną, skupiony na lewych interesach.
 
Data:  23.10
Stawka: 250 zł netto
 
·       Sebek (16) - ofiara przestępców, kadet z klubu judo Adama. Sympatyczny chłopak. 
 
Data:  23.10
Stawka: 250 zł netto
 
·       Mama Sebka (44) - przejęta losem syna matka. Płacząca, pełna empatii, troskliwa. Konieczne PRAWO JAZDY
 
Data:  22. i 23.10
Stawka: 700 zł netto za całość
 
·       Matka Kamy (42) - przejęta losem córki matka. Nieco nerwowa, porywcza, ale kochająca i troskliwa. 
 
Data:  24.10
Stawka: 200 zł netto
 
 
Chętne osoby zapraszam do wysyłania zgłoszeń na adres: casting.outset@interia.pl
W tytule maila proszę o wpisanie nazwy postaci.
W treści maila proszę o zawarcie następujących informacji:
1.           Wiek/wzrost/waga
2.           Nr tel. Do kontaktu
3.           Krótki opis doświadczenia
4.           Linki do sowich materiałów video – demo/wizytówka/scenki castingowe
5.           Aktualne zdjęcie
6.           Informacje o posiadanym i czynnym prawie jazdy lub jego braku
7.           Inormacje o ukończonej szkole aktorskiej/kursach
Nie zwracamy kosztów dojazdu/noclegu

‎Obuh’s world crumbles when her father dies mysteriously and the village insists she cannot inherit because she’s female. But when her father’s ghost appears in a dream, she learns that destiny cannot be buried — even by tradition. ‎

‎A web of greed, betrayal, forbidden love, and faith unfolds as she battles her uncle’s plots, a deceptive stepmother, and a corrupt shrine, until redemption shines through love and divine justice.

* Portretowe selfie w dziennym świetle, na wprost, patrząc w obiektyw. Bez żadnych filtrów. Bez okularów. Bez nakrycia głowy.

items.text:
(Kraków) Szukam ludzi do spektaklu historyczno-poetyckiego, w stylu filmowym, epickim, opartym na życiorysach Tadeusza Borowskiego i Krzysztofa Kamila Baczyńskiego. Premiera przewidziana jest na marzec 2026 roku. Potrzebuję ludzi czujących epokę, poezję, niekoniecznie zawodowców. Poniżej lista postaci, do których szukam aktorów:
* Tadeusz (postać główna, pierwowzór - Tadeusz Borowski i Wincenty Gawron)
* Krzysztof (pierwowzór - K. K. Baczyński)
* Stary Doktor (pierwowzór - Janusz Korczak)
* Kapelan (pierwowzów - ksiądz Tiso)
* Bracia żydowscy Jakub i Izaak
* Roma (żona polskiego oficera)
* Pola (pierwowzór - Barbara Baczyńska)
* Rachela (żydowska dziewczyna, wieszczka, pieśniarka)
* ''Święta'' (handlująca zrabowanymi kosztownościami)
* oficerowie hitlerowscy - Wolf i Jurgen

Chętne osoby zapraszam do kontaktu na priv. Pozdrawiam.

message.text: 🎬✨ Calling Aspiring Creators ✨🌙 White Feather Studios is looking for talented Actors, Entertainers, Dancers, and Models to join our creative collective. We help get our Creators into TV, Film, Modelling, and Live Performance Events, both in the UK and internationally 🌟. If you have the right talent, drive, and presence, we can put your profile forward for high-profile roles and notable projects ✨. If you have the dream, or just want some guidance, this is the place to be, a quality environment for aspiring creators to learn, grow, and find their path. 📩 Reach out to us to JOIN the Collective and start your journey with us ✨  #YourJourney #Collective #Entertainment #Magic  White Feather Studios

Make Up Artist required for studio film shoot in Bolton the weekend of November 15th for our series, Creatives On The Couch. Basic Make Up for the Presenter and also Guests. Approx 11 guests over the 2 days. Onset from 9am until approx 5pm, both days. 

£100 per day, plus IMDb credit, and also well fed on set. 

Experience required AND own transport is a MUST. 

To Apply: INBOX your details to us, your location, if you have OWN transport and relevant experience.

items.text:
I am seeking strong, versatile actors for key supporting roles in my upcoming feature film *EXHIT* — a dark, character-driven psychological thriller set in Manchester. The film explores fate, control, and the descent into chaos after one man’s decision to hire a hitman to end his own life goes catastrophically wrong.

**ROLES**

**Urban Thug #1 – “Rico” (Male, 20s–30s)**
Charismatic and unpredictable. Energetic, naturalistic performer comfortable with improvisation and physicality. Any UK base.
*Required: 3rd–9th November.*

**Urban Thug #2 – “Dez” (Male, 20s–30s)**
Lean, intense, quick-thinking. Brings raw energy and realism; great at reacting in tense, improvised scenes. Any UK base.
*Required: 3rd–9th November.*

**Aisha (Female, 20s–30s)**
Jake’s nurse. Compassionate yet assertive. South Asian or mixed heritage preferred. Strong emotional range and natural chemistry with the lead.
*Required: 3rd–9th November.*
items.title:
STAY TUNE GUYS….!

Rahat Shah,
A talented Fitness Model/Actor/Photographer and British Champion in Men’s Physique from Birmingham, UK! 

Hailing from a renowned art family in Pakistan’s film industry, Rahat’s creative genes are undeniable. With a string of achievements, including winning the British Champion award and Asians Beauty Pageant, Rahat has made a name for himself.

His upcoming Indian thriller film “Second Chance” Directed by Sachin Karande is set to release soon, promising to captivate audiences worldwide.

As a cover model for numerous magazines, Rahat’s charm and physique have won hearts. Through his journey, he aims to inspire others, proving that hard work and dedication can lead to success. Stay tuned for an exciting story of passion, talent, and triumph!

items.text:
CREW CALL – STUDENT SHORT FILM (Unpaid / Non-Union)

Title: Stars Above Us

Shoot Dates: June 5–7, 2026

Location: Bowling Green, KY

We’re seeking passionate and reliable crew members for Stars Above Us, a student drama short film exploring friendship, loss, and mental health. This is a volunteer project—perfect for those looking to gain narrative experience, build credits, and expand reels in a collaborative, professional set environment. All production gear will be provided.

**POSITIONS NEEDED**

Camera Department
* 1st Assistant Camera (Focus Puller)
* Steadicam Operator
* Camera Production Assistants

Grip & Electric (G&E)
* Gaffer
* Grip & Electric
* Swing

Art Department
* Production Designer
* Art Production Assistant

Production Team
* Script Supervisor
* Production Assistants
* Production Manager

Sound Department
* Boom Operator
* Utility Sound

Other Roles
* Hair Stylist
* Makeup Artist
* Storyboard Artist

**TO APPLY**

Please send your information, résumé/reel (if applicable), and the role you’re interested in to:

📧 crewcoordinator.smiletime@gmail.com

Note: If a role is not listed, it has already been filled.

items.text: One of my first short films from 2023 🎥 “Asher Knows”

sharedPost.text:
🎬 Asher Knows
After his father’s sudden death, a young man trapped in a dead-end job is forced into the criminal world his father left behind—but as his choices destroy the people he loves, he must fight to break free and rebuild his life before he’s lost to the same cycle forever.

 A drama short film written and directed by Antoñía Maritza Amp.
Starring: Natalio Seven McGuffie, “Dew” Craig Dewberry, Ro Marcano, Buddy Rowe, Mary Jerome, Romeo & Chad Marcano. FIlmed in June 2023.

🎵 Music Credits 🎵
“Jook” – Bobby Ray Postell
“Litty (Weekend)” – Afterse7en
“Only the Real Ones” (feat. Burga) – 6CO
“Homie Don’t Like Me” – Buddy Rowe
“2 Milly” – Jabba
“Brand New Drip” – Burga
“Nasty” – Grindhard & Dew
“Lifestyle” – YNW Smokedaloc
“Get Thee” (feat. Destiny) – Zion’s Garden 

Special thanks to Lizzys Restaurant and Carabella Wellness Spa for opening their doors and allowing us to film in their spaces.

RIP Craig "Dew" Dewberry 💙💛

MY MOMMA’S ERA: THE MUSICAL – SEEN THROUGH MY MOTHER’S LENS

Saturday, November 8, 2025
Greenwood Oasis Theater – 7621 S. Greenwood Ave, Chicago, IL
Showtime: 7 PM | VIP Experience: 4 PM | Doors Open: 6 PM
FREE PARKING

Come dressed in your best 40s, 50s, 60s, or 70s attire!
(It’s recommended — not required — for the full experience!)

Step back in time and experience a powerful musical journey through the Great Migration, Bronzeville’s rich Black history, and the soul of World War II-era Chicago — told through acting, singing, dancing, and narration.

 Featuring unforgettable portrayals of:
Billie Holiday, Nat King Cole, Ella Fitzgerald, Dinah Washington, Cab Calloway, Etta James
Plus a moving tribute to Minnie Riperton, Chicago’s own.

A dynamic cast. Real stories. Legendary music.
This is more than entertainment — it’s edutainment.

TICKETS & GROUP BENEFITS
Group rates (10+) already discounted online
Call 773-655-3575 for Senior & Youth group discounts!

Eventbrite (Use code: MyMommasEra2025):
 https://www.eventbrite.com/e/my-mommas-era-the-musical-stage-play-tickets-1302271441939?aff=oddtdtcreator

Zeffy (No fees to us!):
 https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/ticketing/my-mommas-era-the-musical-stage-play

 SUPPORT THE MOVEMENT – DONATE TODAY
Dream Real Theatre Company is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit using the arts to educate, inspire, and transform.

Zeffy (tax-deductible):
https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/donation-form/donate-to-make-a-difference-19332

 PayPal:
https://www.paypal.com/donate?hosted_button_id=4HEYR2LBTP8J8

Zelle: 773-655-3575

We're going live to raise funds for Dream Real Theatre Company, and your support is needed to bring productions to life to fund community outreach and mentorship programs and build our future performing media arts training facility.
Your support tonight helps us:

Fund production costs for the show (venue, lighting, costumes, sound, and more)

Launch our Mentors in the Streets program to reach youth through the arts

Build the BSW Performing Arts & Media Center, a home for community creativity and opportunity.

• Bright and quiet environment
• Located in a well-kept building

🔑 Ideal for one person looking for a comfortable, convenient, and modern home in Budapest’s city center.

items.text:
Sziasztok :) 

*Hosszútávon keresek alkalmi statiszta és hostess munkára fiatalokat. *

*Kötöttség nélkül végezhető munkalehetőség. Te osztod be a munka időd ,ezért kényelmesen végezhető egyéb elfoglaltságok mellett is. *

Betöltésre váró pozíciók: 

**- Vendég fogadó hostess  **💃
( konferenciákon, díjátadókon, céges születésnapi partikon stb.) 
***Bérek: nettó 2.000-3.000 / óra***

**- Promóciós hostess **🎈
( a legnépszerűbb hazai és nemzetközi márkák termék kóstoltatásain, nyereményjátékain, kitelepülésein stb.) 
***Bérek: nettó 2.000-3.000 /óra***

(gyerek rendezvényeken, gyere táborokban stb.)

Actors wanted for Dick Whittington, Valley Theatre’s annual seasonal panto.

Audition date and time; 7.15pm, Monday 13th October 2025, at Valley Theatre, Childwall Valley Rd, Liverpool L27 3YA

Performance dates: Sat 17th Jan 2026(afternoon and eve) and Sun 18th Jan 2026 (afternoon only);

Rehearsal days; Monday 7pm whole cast usually; Thursday eve selected scenes.

Valley Theatre’s traditional panto has become legendary in the area. As a community theatre we pride ourselves on keeping the prices family friendly without compromising on the quality. We like to offer a traditional storyline with well-loved panto routines, popular music, up-to-date and local references, strong on humour.

This is a great opportunity for actors wanting to gain unbeatable stage experience with a friendly and supportive production team.

Wide range of parts available for the experienced and beginner alike. No prep needed for the audition.

Please note: this is non-paying.

More details info@valleytheatre.co.uk

**Casting Call UBC Student Film "Sick Days"**

**Non Union, Unpaid, IMDB Credit. **

  Sick Days follows an adventurous, immigrant child who dares to indulge in his fascination of the outdoors despite his own fragile immune system, and his protective single mother's wishes to shield him from the nasty parts of the world — both micro and macroscopic.

**Simon- Lead**

6 to 10, Male, Korean. Bilingual preferred

A timid and optimistic child quick to follow rules but ever curious to break them.

**Holly- Lead**

30s, female, korean. Fluent in Korean

A paranoid yet tender helicopter parent, shielding her son from the world.

**Anthony- Supporting**

6 to 10, Fun loving, extroverted kid, searching for camaraderie in a lonely new city.

Submit a Headshot and any supporting materials (demo-reel or self-tapes) to sickdays.film@gmail.com

Specific Shoot dates are tentative, but will either be December 6-8, or 13-15.

items.text:
# **Model Casting Call — Skincare Facial Content Shoot (Paid)**

**Date:** Monday, October 13th, 2025
**Time:** 11 AM – 4 PM (1-2-hour time slots per model)
**Location:** Studio in Kitsilano *(exact address will be shared with confirmed models)*
**Compensation:** **$100 total for 1-2 hours (plus a complimentary facial)**

Hi everyone! I’m Brianna, an esthetician creating skincare and facial content for my portfolio. I’m looking for** 3 models (any gender, 18+)** to take part in a calm facial treatment shoot.

**Shoot details:**
✨ Gentle, soothing facial in a relaxing environment 💆🏻‍♀️
✨ Makeup-free, clean skin look
✨ Filmed with a** photographer and videographer**
✨ Videos/stills used for social media 
✨ You’ll receive edited images for your portfolio

✨ Glowy skin and compliments from friends will follow ;)

**Requirements:**
• Comfortable on camera, makeup-free
• No major skin sensitivities or allergies (we will do a consultation before)
• Punctual, communicative, and reliable

• Modelling/acting experience is a plus!

**To apply:**
Please PM me with the following:
• Your name, a short intro, and your contact information
• A recent natural photo of your face
• Confirmation you’re available on **Monday, Oct 13 (between 11 AM – 4 PM)**

• Optional: if you want to link your socials, send your resume, attach your portfolio or a video, you're more than welcome to, I support creativity :)

This will be a relaxing, paid opportunity — perfect for anyone wanting **beauty or skincare portfolio content** in a modern, minimal style 🌸

Kindly note, I will be reaching out to selected talent only. Thank you for your interest and time, and I look forward to reviewing applications!

sharedPost.text:
Zemsta chorego człowieka.

Jak już sama, czy też sam wiesz, to tydzień temu pewien pedofil, który był dość mocno poirytowany naszymi poczynaniami, założył Maciejowi i mi profil na stronie maxmodels.pl. Ten numer zrobił nam drugi raz. Wahałem się dość mocno, czy to w ogóle zgłosić, jednakże namówiliście mnie. Dlaczego się wahałem? Otóż taki ostatni numer zrobił mi w listopadzie tamtego roku. Wtedy zgłosiłem to od razu dowiedziawszy się o samym fakcie od samego pedofila. Wtedy było to konto „Marcelina Marcelina”, czyli to samo, które całkiem niedawno miało swój post ostrzegawczy i w końcu całkowicie zniknęło.

Sam numer wyglądał dość typowo, bo pedofil wpierw założył mi wspomniany profil. Później, aby mi bardziej zaszkodzić, wykorzystał do tego konto, które już wcześniej zapewne wykorzystywał do podobnych czynów. Wtedy na zdjęciu profilowym miał dziewczę, które na czole miało błyskawicę, obraną za symbol walki o prawo do aborcji. W jaki sposób wykorzystał to konto? Otóż na kilku grupach związanych z dziećmi, a w tym jednej zagranicznej, publikował posty, gdzie była informacja na mój temat, podając link do tegoż maxmodels. Wdał się nawet ze mną w dyskusję na grupie o fejkach, za co dostał zawieszenie, gdyż trudno tak normalnie z dewiantem gadać.

Konto to po pewnym czasie ucichło, a nawet zostało skasowane. Problem polega na tym, że już wtedy wiedziałem, że to sam „on”. Typ wyraźnie mnie nie docenił. Po drodze trafił mi się nawet sygnał od pewnej małoletniej, że pedofil pisze z tegoż konta przedstawiając się jako „Katarzyna Kw”. O tej części będzie mam nadzieję, że szerzej dopiero jutro, ale na tym etapie wtedy sprawę zgłosiłem. Uczyniłem też tak samo w niedzielę tydzień temu, w sprawie drugiego zdarzenia. Dlaczego się jednak wahałem, czy w ogóle to zrobić? Otóż niestety popełniłem błąd za pierwszym razem, gdyż chciałem to zrobić jak najszybciej. Nie zrobiłem np. tego, co teraz, czyli nie opisałem całej sprawy na spokojnie będąc zasadniczo na komisariacie tylko dosłuchany z zakresu tego, co opisałem poniekąd w swojego rodzaju raporcie. Powiedziano mi jednak wtedy, że zawsze mogę sprawę opisać i donieść w późniejszym czasie, ale tak jak to uczyniłem, tak nie zostało to raczej wzięte pod uwagę. Dlaczego? Wyobraźcie sobie, że ktoś tak wykorzystuje Wasze zdjęcie, podaje namiary na Was i zamieszcza kilka zdjęć małoletnich dziewczynek. Teraz wyobraźcie sobie, że dostałem list polecony z informacją, że jest odmowa wszczęcia postępowania z uwagi na brak znamion czynu zabronionego. Z resztą widać to w postaci zdjęcia dokumentu, który otrzymałem. Tak samo teraz wątpię, aby było to inaczej załatwione.

Co do reszty, to fejkowy profil Macieja i mój zniknął dopiero w poniedziałek, kiedy to został ujawniony. Zniknął, kiedy tamtejsi admini przyszli do pracy. Zniknął, kiedy mogli skorzystać z kompetencji, które im przekazano jako narzędzia pracy (bo mam nadzieję, że są ambitni), które to kompetencje są dość niedorzeczne. Drogie MaxModels. Rozumiem, że macie to w dupie i rozumiem, że spotkanie, o którym wspominał Maciej w fejkowym profilu było na pokaz, ale serio? Jeśli ktoś zamieści tam zdjęcie przedstawiające np. gwałt, albo zwłoki, to też je opublikujecie? Nigdy nie będzie zatwierdzania ogłoszeń?

Należy też jednocześnie wspomnieć o czymś dość ważnym dla sprawy. Ilość odwiedzin tegoż fejkowego profilu, to około 350 ciekawskich. Ilość odwiedzin postu, w którym wspominam o sprawie to 16438 osób. Innymi słowy, to jak już wspominałem Ci wcześniej, gdy pisałeś z konta „Marcelina Marcelina”, to jesteś dla mnie za mały. Kolejną sprawą, którą trzeba tutaj poruszyć jest wykorzystane zdjęcie. Wcześniej były to zdjęcia małoletnich dziewczynek np. z odsłoniętymi piersiami, czy też w pozach nacechowanych seksualnie, a tło miało charakter studyjny. Zdjęcia te można było też odnaleźć na serwerach rosyjskich. Obecne, które przedstawia chłopca w czerwonych bokserkach nie ma takiego wyniku w ogóle. Świadczy to m.in. o tym, że wątpliwym jest stwierdzenie, aby należało ono to tzw. grupy „child love”, gdyż gdzie jest reszta (określenie związane z tzw. „pozytywna pedofilią”, na która jest paragraf)? Ewentualnie, ponieważ zdjęcie zostało wykonane w specyficzny sposób (Chłopiec „na kolanach” opiera się na oparciu fotela mając zamknięte oczy, głowa poprzez lewy policzek dotyka górnej części wspomnianego oparcia. Na fotelu widać górną część marynarki koloru beżowego oraz spodnie także od marynarki, ale razem nie stanowią zestawu w kolorystycznym znaczeniu. Drzwi od balkonu drewniane i w połowie z drewna, a druga połowa to szyba i są uchylone. Klamka aluminiowa. Parapet ze „sztucznego kamienia” i grzejnik pod nim. Drewniana podłoga, ale nie panele. Stare budownictwo.) należy założyć, że jest częścią dłuższej sesji. Chłopiec wyraźnie pozował, a fotografem była osoba zdecydowanie starsza, co widać po ubiorze. Nie można jasno określić daty jego powstania, ale w lewym, dolnym jak i prawym rogu są zapewne produkty spożywcze mogące w jakiś sposób naprowadzić na datę. Samo zdjęcie, ponieważ zdecydowanie pochodzi z prywatnej grupy, do której nie ma dostępu z zewnątrz, z pewnością ma jak już wspomniałem swój dalszy ciąg w postaci serii zapisanej przez sprawcę. On sam może być też jego autorem, ale to już tylko gdybanie, bo dlaczego zamieścił tylko jeden obraz?

Na ten czas jak już wspomniałem, sprawa jest zgłoszona. Nie spodziewam się telefonu z informacją „mamy go”, ale epizod ten traktuję jako eksperyment i bardzo chciałbym Was o jego zakończeniu poinformować. Przepraszam też za dość dużą zwłokę, ale nie samym FB żyje.

**‼WARSZAWA - REKLAMA SAMOCHODU 🚗‼**

Szukamy statystów do reklamy samochodu na terenie Warszawy!

**TERMIN**: jeden dzień zdjęciowy w dniach 25–29 października (dokładny dzień zostanie potwierdzony, ale szukamy osób **dyspozycyjnych **na te wszystkie dni!)

**STAWKA:**

– 170 zł – jeśli plan zacznie się przed 6:00 rano;

– 160 zł – jeśli plan zacznie się po 6:00 rano.

Szukamy:

Mężczyzn 35–55lat – dla jednego wybranego Pana przymiarki 23.10, płatne dodatkowo 50 zł

Kobiet i mężczyzn w różnym wieku – RÓŻNE TYPY, PEŁEN PRZEKRÓJ!

**ZGŁOSZENIA:**

proszę wysłać zgłoszenie na maila dominika@podtytulem.pl

Tytuł maila: REKLAMA 25-29

W treści maila: imię i nazwisko, wiek, wzrost, miejsce zamieszkania, 2 aktualne zdjęcia (twarz + sylwetka)!

‼️ WARSZAWA 11 PAŹDZIERNIKA ‼️

Na plan serialu kryminalnego, którego akcja dzieje się w latach współczesnych, poszukujemy statystów do sceny pogrzebu:

▪️ KOBIET i MĘŻCZYZN w wieku ok 18-70 lat 

▪️ eleganckich MĘŻCZYZN do małych epizodów kontynuacyjnych (27.10)

Wyjazd godz. 5 z centrum lub dojazd własny na godz. 7 (Antoninów). Plan ma nie być całodniowy. Stawka dla statystów 140zł gotówką po planie, dla epizodów 400zł gotówką po drugim dniu zdjęciowym. 

Zgłoszenia wraz z imieniem i nazwiskiem, numerem telefonu, AKTUALNYMI zdjęciami (sylwetka, twarz), przyjmujemy na adres: CASTING@ONSETAGENCY.PL w tytule wpisując „CMENTARZ”.

🎪 𝐀𝐄𝐑𝐈𝐀𝐋 𝐏𝐄𝐑𝐅𝐎𝐑𝐌𝐄𝐑 𝐀𝐕𝐀𝐈𝐋𝐀𝐁𝐋𝐄 — 𝐂𝐇𝐑𝐈𝐒𝐓𝐌𝐀𝐒 & 𝐍𝐎𝐕 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 – 𝐌𝐀𝐑 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟔   🎪

Hello everyone! 👋
My name is Lina, I’m an aerial performer from Ukraine, based in Europe 

✅ Acts available:

• 𝗛𝗮𝗶𝗿 & 𝗧𝗲𝗲𝘁𝗵 𝗦𝘂𝘀𝗽𝗲𝗻𝘀𝗶𝗼𝗻
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1yCPXNyx452y6AOr29oj43tuwFeuCiCaJ/view?usp=drivesdk

• 𝗔𝗲𝗿𝗶𝗮𝗹 𝗛𝗼𝗼𝗽
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1g8VSTvDeimz_UqsUe-oaIxq28iM6FJ0f/view?usp=drivesdk

• 𝗔𝗲𝗿𝗶𝗮𝗹 𝗟𝗼𝗼𝗽𝘀
https://drive.google.com/file/d/14l7LbLMZoTPgoqNxMCRU-W7eltvtC-5P/view?usp=drivesdk

• 𝗔𝗲𝗿𝗶𝗮𝗹 𝗛𝗮𝗺𝗺𝗼𝗰𝗸
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1jCW6CUReq4EL5HECyJ34NiMEY2_x_NtF/view?usp=drivesdk

I’m now open for bookings for 𝗖𝗵𝗿𝗶𝘀𝘁𝗺𝗮𝘀 𝘀𝗲𝗮𝘀𝗼𝗻 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟲 - gala shows, dinner shows, circus productions, theatres - if there’s a stage (or a rig), I’m in.

📩 𝗢𝗽𝗲𝗻 𝘁𝗼 𝗰𝗼𝗹𝗹𝗮𝗯𝗼𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻𝘀, 𝗮𝗴𝗲𝗻𝗰𝗶𝗲𝘀, 𝗽𝗿𝗼𝗱𝘂𝗰𝗲𝗿𝘀 & 𝗰𝗿𝗮𝘇𝘆 𝗶𝗱𝗲𝗮𝘀

+++ Darsteller (m/w) leicht curvy für Imageclip Bank  +++

WAS SUCHEN WIR:

Für ein Clipdreh für eine Bank vom 27. bis 30. Oktober suchen wir für unseren Kunden einen Darsteller für die Rolle von Kunden in einer Bank. Es wird evtl. eine Minikleine Sprechrolle sein.

WANN: Montag 27.10.2025 - Donnerstag 30.10.2025 ( EIN DREHTAG )

WO:  Raum Frankfurt / Mannheim

WAS:  Videoclip für regionale Bank

HONORAR:

+ 600 Euro

+ Anreisekosten

+ Übernachtung

Voraussetzungen:

-          Alter ca. 35-55 Jahre

-          Leicht Curvy / 

-          Typ "Normaler" Bankkunde

-          Erfahrung im Bereich Imagefilmdreh

Bewerbungen & Fragen bitte bis 12.10.2025 - 12:00 Uhr an: jobs@fishershouse.de

Bitte schickt uns direkt 4-5 passende Fotos von euch mit, damit wir uns einen Eindruck von euch machen können.

Schickt uns bitte außerdem die Information, an welchen Tagen im Zeitraum ihr Verfügbar wärt.

Wir schauen uns alle Bewerbungen an. Wenn wir denken, dass ihr passen können. Schicken wir euch eine kleine Mail mit der Bitte ein kurzes Video nachzuspielen.

Wir freuen uns auf eure Bewerbungen

items.text:
**STATISTER SØGES TIL KORTFILM**

Vi er en gruppe på Masterclass - Potemkin, den jyske filmskole, som er igang med et kortfilmsprojekt, og til det søger vi 7-8 statister.

Statisterne skal bruges til en scene i parken, som baggrundsfolk og af denne grund søger vi folk af alle aldre og køn.

**Praktisk info:**

Jobbet er ulønnet og optagelserne vil tage sted d. 21. eller 22. oktober i Viby.

**LOGLINE:**

Kortfilmen er en symbolsk film om den unge hjemmehjælper, Laura, som møder en ældre kvinde, der lod livets muligheder smuldre væk. Mødet bliver et spejl, der tvinger Laura til at vælge, om hun selv vil tage en bid af livet - eller lade tiden gå

Ved interesse så kontakt endelig vores producer, Hjalte:

**Hjalte2001@gmail.com**

Statister til musikvideo - ULØNNET

Hej alle, vi leder efter nogle statister til en musikvideo vi filmer i et sommerhus i Hornbæk d. 25 oktober. Det skal filmes i et one-take. 
Vi søger mænd og kvinder i alderen mellem 20 og 30 år. 

Vi sørger for mad, drikkevarer og transportomkostninger, og kan hente og bringe i bil fra og til Espergærde Station. 
Der vil også serveres drinks efter. 

Lad mig vide hvis det er interessant :-)

Kontakt mig på Facebook eller +4531175111

Venligst,
Jacob

items.text:
Hello! We are shooting an unpaid improvised short film next week from the 15th to the 18th of October based on the concept for our feature film SOPHIE, and we are looking for an actor for one for the lead roles, to play a charismatic pubcrawl guide (25-35, Male) with a dark side. Shooting will take place on the 15th, 16th, 17th and 18th of October, all night shoots.

If you're interested in knowing more details please send me your showreel or a short introductory video of you and your acting experience, to vasco.cinema.2018@gmail.com.

Sinopsis: On a weekend escape to Copenhagen, Sophie reunites with an old friend and spirals through a night of fleeting connections, as she’s forced to confront the cost of trying to feel anything at all.

items.text:
ACTORS & CREW & LOCATIONS WANTED – NO-BUDGET GRADUATION FILM (English / Multilingual)

I am Nadja, 26, nearing the completion of my acting degree at Cours Florent (Macromedia) in Berlin, and I am looking for ambitious people for **IN FRONT OF** and **BEHIND** the camera.

**Shooting Period:** November 1st – November 5th in Berlin

**Budget:** None, however, we have launched a Crowdfunding campaign to create a high-quality short film (max. 15min) that will be submitted to international festivals.

The short film explores a theme that has preoccupied me my entire life: my cultural identity. Am I German? Am I Polish? Can I be both and unite these parts? How much do I owe my parents, who sacrificed so much to enable a better life for me? The film is about four people caught between tradition and their own path, struggling with what the right way forward is. The film will illuminate Polish, Vietnamese, Turkish, and German culture.

**Casting: Roles Still to be Filled (1/2 – 1 shooting day per role)**

**Anna's Father (Jerzy)**

Mid-50s – Mid-60s; Must speak **Polish**

The Polish immigrant (blue-collar background) who works in a skillful, crafty trade. Driven by the high educational aspirations common among Polish migrants in Germany, he relentlessly pushed Anna toward the *Gymnasium* track and high-status academic success. Must convey **conflicted pride** and strict, yet wounded, authority.

**Linh's Mother (Hoa)**

Mid-50s – Mid-60s; Must speak **Vietnamese**

She is **stern and formidable** and places great importance on external appearance and family honor. Her strictness stems from a deep-seated fear that Linh's assimilation will lead to disrespect for the ancestors and personal instability. She **micromanages Linh's appearance**, demanding conservative dress and traditional feminine conduct. 

**Onur's Mother**

Approx. 60; Must speak **Turkish**

Her life’s priority is the **continuation of the family lineage**, viewing marriage and children as the absolute purpose of life and success. She is completely **oblivious to Onur's true sexuality** and confronts him with a young woman she considers "perfect." Must convey powerful, traditional authority mixed with subtle, genuine softness.

**Onur's Aunt (Leman)**

Approx. 50; Must speak **Turkish**

Onur’s charismatic and modern aunt, who serves as a vital contrast to the Mother. Leman is wittier, more open, and has a less rigid approach to life in the diaspora. She represents a more assimilated perspective and offers a relaxed energy that provides a potential emotional refuge from family pressure.

**Chris**

Approx. 30 – 35; Scene involves **light intimacy** (NO nudity or partial nudity!)

An **athletic, highly attractive businessman** who operates in Anna’s world of luxury and efficiency. He is polished, charismatic, and carries the effortless confidence of someone who could model formal attire. Initially perceived as a "sex-only" casual date, Chris is actually calm and emotionally perceptive, pushing for a **genuine connection** after six months of casual encounters.

**Crew and Location Search**

We are also looking for comprehensive help on set and in post-production.

**Location Search:**
* We primarily seek a large apartment with an **open-plan kitchen/living area** where we can film the main scene.
* For 1 scene, we are looking for a **Vietnamese restaurant** where we could potentially film for a few hours **BEFORE** the shop opens. No extras or food are needed, just the interior of the restaurant.
* An apartment with a **balcony** where we can film a scene with three people (ideally a *Plattenbau* setting).

If interested, please send an email to: [lostintranslationproduction@gmail.com](mailto:lostintranslationproduction@gmail.com)  or [info@nadja-gallera.de](mailto:info@nadja-gallera.de)

Thank you very much for your attention and help.

Best regards!
